Class SetUpGameController

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.iit.sat.itmd4515.rbalasubramanian1.web.SetUpGameController
  • @Named
@RequestScoped
public class SetUpGameController
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a backing bean to handle Game functionality to teams. A game is not assigned to all the teams by default. A coach of a team, sets up a game against another team for a given date.

    raghul
